  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "I vote YES on this treasury withdrawal because the proposal addresses a core infrastructure need: stronger node diversity and resilience for Cardano, with a defined 2026 scope. My decision is based on governance discipline as much as technical value, so funding must remain tied to milestone-based payouts, objective acceptance criteria, and transparent public reporting of delivery and spending. The requested amount is significant, which makes strict accountability essential throughout execution. If these safeguards are not upheld, future support should be reconsidered."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}